Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:41.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:52.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:59.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:06.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:13.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:17.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:19.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:27.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:34.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:40.91,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:52.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:59.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能换人不再悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:41.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我宁愿舍弃笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:45.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}她说着低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:52.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这一夜 我流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:59.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冰冷彻骨 仿如冻雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:06.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}洒落的现实 无处可避
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:13.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:17.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅为这理由而束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:19.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Heart  My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:27.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪光对面 看到了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:34.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的窗上 映出旧时晴空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:40.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽无法如鸟儿一般飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:54.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为铭记谁人悲伤之时的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:59.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}轻轻闭上双眼 哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:14.07,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(163,360)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}反抗的凯歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就算是人质了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖别动…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗 席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这首歌是玛莉娜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 为什么能听到歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:42.62,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}お金があっても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:47.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}友だちは買えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:53.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}なにもなくてもね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:59.46,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}みんながいるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:04.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}みんな聞いて　僕たちの夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:10.71,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}みんな知って　僕たちを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:15.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}あなたはどうしてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:21.56,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}僕はね元気だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:27.15,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}あなたはどうしてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:33.28,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}僕はね元気だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:42.62,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}纵使家财万贯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:47.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}也买不到友情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:53.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}即使一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:59.46,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}仍有大家陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:04.89,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}大家来倾听 我们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:10.71,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}大家来知晓 我们的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:15.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}你过得如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:21.56,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}我很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:27.15,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}你过得如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:33.28,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}我很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到布林居然挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的话我来安慰你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因愤怒而颤抖 为布林·斯塔比利的不中用而气愤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者居然被打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚·艾迪似乎选择了与我们敌对的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得这很美妙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有MS接近?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是A-LAWS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛…玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人 快叫医务兵来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E探测器 光学摄影机皆无反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这空域似乎没有联邦军布阵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去汇合地点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的补给部队似乎已到达了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得感谢提供情报的KATARON啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会转达的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也谢谢莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之能修的地方先修吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢协助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 用了Seraphim啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则就被变革者的机体打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们察觉到Seraphim的特性了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 得先接受KATARON的补给 脱离联邦包围网才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在托勒密的武器管制系统不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS来了我们可不是对手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有00-Raiser就能打破这种局面…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到达汇合地点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政变的主谋是你?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦议会无视舆论 创立独立治安维持部队 扩大军事实力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至使用了卫星武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能对其所作所为视而不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没小看他们 就算是A-LAWS 也有无法涉足的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非要将轨道升降机…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我也参加政变?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会违抗军队纪律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则赫利也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来拜访你是想让你别插手此事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我睁一只眼闭一只眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作为军人 而是以长年的友人身份拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想与你作对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈库里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟尔盖 你以前说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队是为保护国民和国家利益 作为对外势力的威慑力量而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在错误的政局下 军队无法正常发挥功能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想在正确的军队中作为军人而活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你们不能将政变开始的时间地点告诉KATARON?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为防止情报泄露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望KATARON看到我们的奋斗 再决定是否协助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要事先协助?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切由我们自行解决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我会将你们的事告知各支部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会通知天人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有联络手段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他们有对抗A-LAWS的战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为有邀请他们协助的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过 我相信他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 这的确是为数不多的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚降落地上又要作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 你就不想更为女性化一些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在那个叫沙慈的人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已舍弃过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你应该也舍弃复仇之心…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱启蒙就交给本大爷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能像我们一样意志相通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来雷杰尼不参加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官大人驾到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以人类来说算有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候多时了 玛内金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS开发部的毕利·片桐技术上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将在本舰上打扰一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术人员怎么会来现场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想亲眼见证天人毁灭的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经获得司令的许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这愿望很快就能实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这等战力 就不需要什么小花招了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个了结吧 九条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS几乎倾全力对付天人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 就让我利用一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=============================================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这栋房子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把生命献给真主 参加这次圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为被真主认可 被真主庇护的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:10:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了保护真主的教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上没有真主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的 只是一种产生暴力的卑劣仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放他走出家门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 过去只能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己现在的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他都不会被改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说他人的心情 更何况是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:55.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}なくす事が拾うためなら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:12:01.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}別れるのは出逢うため
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:06.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}「さようなら」のあとには　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:12.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}「こんにちは」と出逢うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:23.28,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}緑色芝生に寝ころんでいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:55.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}若失去是为了寻回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:12:01.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}别离就是为了相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:06.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}告别之后 一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:12.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}邂逅你的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:23.28,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}多想躺在那翠绿草坪上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 你要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替没能改变的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌…这首歌是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜 这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜 刚才我听到的歌是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这些孩子的心愿编成歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在TRANS-AM中听到这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子弹虽然取出了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可没有细胞活性装置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只有疗伤这段时间也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前 你给我的信上这么写着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找人与人能够互相理解的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先得从互相认知开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点时间总需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔们要去打仗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但正在做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这要看运气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别当真回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里危险 回房去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在亲热
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库尔吉斯战争时 你竟然有过这种经历
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10多年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨战争的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在随处可见的普通家庭中长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾想过往那方面发展
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被选为了阿撒迪斯坦的皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是一国的皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹奏音乐会更适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是在勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你也同样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强自己 进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情报说你的母舰在欧洲支部进行了补给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠KATARON调配来的补给物资
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外壁的修补工作即将完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算能赶在敌人来之前搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是潜水模式还用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器管制系统也还有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续作业
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 幸好有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方MS队朝本舰接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从粒子释放量看 敌人部队为A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如艾纽所说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人完全掌握了我们的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 敌人数量有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人总数36架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36架?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎还有新型MA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾巢而出了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 依次出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密以山脉为掩护撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 为什么不让我去驾驶MS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说你有不死之身的绰号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借你运势一用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知全员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰有伤在身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gadessa和Empruss拖住Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他机体专心攻击敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一战送他们回老家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然超出Gadessa的射程
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先制攻击削减其数量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 别舍不得粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来狙击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这粒子光束的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是TRANS-AM系统的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 全机散开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的攻击有极限时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前不许贸然靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达极限时间 到达极限时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达成指标
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充填结束前就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚 提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚 别让敌人靠近托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机突击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样直奔敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 Gundam来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的对手在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给人反击的空隙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子装填中 GN粒子装填中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方部队接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离射程0034
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武装用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下GN-Archer
